 class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"rlcfj\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box  \">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p>\n<span class=\"icon-video\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/233447934\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"aMRP0\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable border\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None background ng-touched\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Tying</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"uzd1j\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box  \">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p>\n<span class=\"icon-video\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/233448017\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"Z2ZAK\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5 class=\"background\">Bundling</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"Pa0KZ\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box  \">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p>\n<span class=\"icon-video\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/233448081\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"0AjfQ\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed ui-resizable  \">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>the main points from this module are as follows:</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"ORIhe\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\">\n<div class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched fontNormal\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\"><b>Price discrimination:</b> selling the same product at different rates.</li><li class=\"\">These price differences reflect variations in the elasticity of demand for these different groups. When demand curves are different, it is more profitable to set different prices in different markets.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Perfect price discrimination</b>: market is segmented so that each person is charged their maximum willingness to pay.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\">In this scenario, consumers end up with zero consumer surplus and all the gains from trade go to the monopolist. Also, there is no deadweight loss.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Tying </b>is a form of price discrimination in which one good, called the based good, is tied to a second good called the variable good.<br></li><li class=\"\">The base good is generally cheap (close to MC) and the tied good is priced at above MC.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\">Tying tends to increase social welfare because it will typically increase output.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Bundling: </b>&nbsp;requiring that products be bought together in a bundle or package.</li><li class=\"\">Bundling increases profits; some of the increase in profit comes from reductions in consumer surplus and from reductions in deadweight loss.&nbsp;<br></li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"9pS6L\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed ui-resizable  \">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Upon completion of this module, you will be able to:</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"hyfgw\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\">\n<div class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched fontNormal\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Discuss the marginal product of labor.</li><li class=\"\">Express an opinion on the purpose of education, either as signalling or skill building.<br></li><li class=\"\">Discuss how unions can either lower or raise wages.<br></li><li class=\"\">Explain why less exciting and more dangerous jobs tend to pay more.<br></li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"VcD27\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"head