editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable border\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None background ng-touched\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Compensating Differentials</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"BOcwq\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box  \">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p>\n<span class=\"icon-video\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/233448547\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"yQHNW\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Do Unions Raise Wages?</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"utGLm\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box  \">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p>\n<span class=\"icon-video\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/233448599\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"o68C0\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed ui-resizable  \">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>The main points from this module are as follows:</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"ZmrZM\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\">\n<div class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched fontNormal\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\"><b>Marginal product of labor:</b> the increase in a firm’s revenues created by hiring an additional labourer.</li><li class=\"\">The marginal product of labor declines as more labor is used.<br></li><li class=\"\">Firms will hire as long as wages are less than the marginal product of labor.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Human capital: </b>&nbsp;tools of the mind, the stuff in people’s heads that makes them productive.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Education</b> is one of the biggest investments people make to increase their human capital.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>College educations</b> signal: IQ, conscientiousness, ability to work with others, grit.<br></li><li class=\"\">Firms have an incentive to increase job safety, because then they can lower wages.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\">Jobs that are more dangerous or less fun tend to generate higher wages.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Unions</b> have the ability to restrict the supply of labor to a job, which can increase wages for some workers. However, unions can also lower wages. For example, work stoppages and strikes supported by unions can slow down economic growth, lowering real wages.<br></li><li class=\"\">Unions can lower wages, as workers not hired in the unionized industries seek employment in other industries.&nbsp;</li><li class=\"\">Unions can be useful in protecting workers from arbitrary abuses and maintain good employee relationships.<br></li><li class=\"\">Work stoppages and strikes can slow down economic growth.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\">Professional associations are essentially unions.</li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"b7RDJ\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed ui-resizable  \">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Upon completion of this module, you will be able to:</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"xk3VZ\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\">\n<div class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched fontNormal\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Differentiate between non-rival, non-excludable, rival, and excludable goods and resources.</li><li class=\"\">Define public, club, and common goods.<br></li><li class=\"\">Discuss free and forced riders.<br></li><li class=\"\">Explain the tragedy of the commons.<br></li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"pEAKs\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Public Goods and Asteroid Defense</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"stjTh\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box  \">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the