<b>Public goods</b> are non-rival and non-excludable.&nbsp;</li><li class=\"\"><b>Non-excludable </b>means that people who do not pay cannot be easily prevented from using the good.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Non-rival </b>means that one person’s use of the good doesn’t reduce the ability of another person to use the good.&nbsp;</li><li class=\"\">Public goods can be produced by taxation and government provision.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Free riders</b> are people who not pay even though they benefit.<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Forced riders</b> are people who do pay even though they do not benefit.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\">Public goods are not exclusively produced by the government or public sector.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Club goods</b> are non-rival and excludable.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\"><b>Common goods </b>are non-excludable and rival.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\">The <b>tragedy of the commons</b> is the tendency of any resource that is unowned to be overused and undermaintained.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\">Remedies include: command and control, cultural norms, and creating property rights.<br></li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"kaEQY\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Upon completion of this module, you will be able to:</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"hMA8u\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\">\n<div class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched fontNormal\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Define adverse selection and asymmetrical information.&nbsp;</li><li class=\"\">Discuss situations when asymmetrical information might be present.<br></li><li class=\"\">Define moral hazard.<br></li><li class=\"\">Discuss ways that moral hazard can be avoid.&nbsp;<br></li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"XNa6g\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Asymmetric Information and Used Cars</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"1ZWoo\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box  \">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p>\n<span class=\"icon-video\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/233449130\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"Jc2T3\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Asymmetric Information in Health Insurance</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"O6uql\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box  \">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in th