curs when an offer conveys negative information about what is being offered.&nbsp;</li><li class=\"\">For example, in market for used cars, sellers have more information about the car’s quality than buyers. However, the market has developed solutions such as warrantees, guarantees, branding, and inspections to offset information asymmetry.<br></li><li class=\"\">A <b>signal </b>is an action that reveals information.<br></li><li class=\"\">Sometimes, when one party has an information advantage, they may have an incentive to exploit the other party. This type of exploitation is called <b>moral hazard.</b><br></li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"DWX0p\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list paragraph, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"editable p-asset ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty fontNormal None\">Some methods for reducing moral hazard include:</div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"Omz8k\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty fontNormal None\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Make information less asymmetric<br></li><li class=\"\">Online rating and reviews<br></li><li class=\"\">Split the diagnosis from the solution<br></li><li class=\"\">Alter the payment structure<br></li><li class=\"\">Encourage ethical approaches, such as the Hippocratic Oath.<br></li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"5LSli\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed ui-resizable  \">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Upon completion of this module, you will be able to:</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"yO5lt\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\">\n<div class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-not-empty None ng-touched fontNormal\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Define consumption, utility, and substitution.</li><li class=\"\">Explain the marginal rate of substitution.&nbsp;<br></li><li class=\"\">Describe the indifference curve.<br></li></ul></div>\n<div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"cPpkB\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Introduction to Consumer Choice</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"wVYhl\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list active, listed selected-class video-box  \">\n<div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None\">\n<div class=\"video-content\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p>\n<span class=\"icon-video\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\">\n<iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/233450146\"></iframe>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li>\n</ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ui-sortable ng-not-empty\">\n<li id=\"eF2P2\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\">\n<div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-not-empty None background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Budget Constraints</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div>